  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: cb567088341fa3c4b9b5217e379ebde5, type: 3}
  m_Name: ShopkeeperDialogue_Greet
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueText
  speakerName: 'Shopkeeper Tokang '
  lines:
  - Hey, you over there, you seem like the kind of-...
  - Wait... I recognize that armour.
  - You're from The Box, are you not? Long time since I've seen one of you around
    here.
  - Figured you'd just stopped caring about anything out here.
  - If you're here, there must be something you're looking for, correct?
  - 'Well, I''m not the folk to help out someone from The Box. '
  - But I need to make business, so if you're willing to pay, I'll aid you as I can.
  - You seem less threatening than other Box Agents, so come over here so we can
    talk better.
